{"article_id":"Ul37Vg41NQlsAfTM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell has received some surprise support","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"just when he needed it most .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"McConnell","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"( R-KY )","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"now has enough votes","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to stop Democrat demands","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to require additional witnesses to testify at the beginning of President Trump 's impeachment trial ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"according to The Hill .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Two moderate GOP senators , Susan Collins of Maine and Lisa Murkowski of Alaska are backing McConnell ' s plan","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"to defer a decision","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to call witnesses in the Senate trial .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"This comes","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"as Trump 's former National Security Adviser John Bolton announced","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"he will testify","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"if called .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Bolton issued a statement","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"saying ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` If the Senate issues a subpoena for my testimony ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"I am prepared to testify . ''","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"It takes a majority vote to call witnesses ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"since the GOP has a 53 seat majority ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"McConnell has the upper hand","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"in deciding whether to call Bolton and others .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"`` The House may have been content to scrap their own norms","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to hurt President Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"but that is not the Senate , ''","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"McConnell said .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"He says","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"the Senate should follow the precedent of the 1999 Clinton impeachment trial .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"That means waiting until later in the process","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"to take up the question","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"of calling additional witnesses .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"says","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"the Senate should agree now to call witnesses .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"`` If any Senate Republican opposes issuing subpoenas to the four witnesses and documents","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"we 've requested ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"they would make it absolutely clear","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"they are participating in a cover-up , ''","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Schumer said .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Meanwhile , House Speaker Nancy Pelosi still has n't delivered the articles of impeachment to the Senate .","depth":3},{"id":43,"text":"On Sunday , Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"told Fox News","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"that the Republican-controlled Senate should change the rules","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"to override Pelosi .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Graham said ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"`` Well , we 're not going to let Nancy Pelosi use the rules of the Senate to her advantage .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"This is dangerous for the presidency as an institution . ''","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"President Trump tweeted this week ,","depth":3},{"id":52,"text":"`` The impeachment hoax , just a continuation of the witch hunt","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"which started","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"even before I won the election ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"must end quickly -","depth":5},{"id":56,"text":"get this done . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":113,"left":98,"right":112,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":58,"right":97,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":58,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":